488cfad1-ad70-411b-af99-de83626bd3d1.description=Checks to see if a date and time occurred recently. The operator will then send an email detailing whether the date/time combination occurred recently.\n\nInputs\:\nthreshold - the number of milliseconds ago that still qualifies as recently.\ndateTime - the date to check, in Jul 12, 2006 4\:23\:20 PM format\nemailHost - the SMTP host to use when sending email.\nemailPort - the SMTP port to use when sending email.\nemailFrom - the email address the message will come from.\nemailTo - the email address the message will go to.\nsubject - the subject of the email.\nbody - the body of the email message.\ncheckName - the name of the value being checked. Will be used in email message generation.\nemailRecent - If set to false emails will not be sent it the event occurred recently, otherwise they will be.\nemailNotRecent - If set to false emails will not be sent it the event did not occur recently, otherwise they will be.\nemailFailed - If set to false emails will not be sent if the flow fails, otherwise they will be.\n\nResponses\:\nrecent - The event ran recently.\nnotRecent - The event has not run recently.\nfailure - The operation failed.\n\n\n\nreturns\:\nthe number of milliseconds ago the event occurred.\n 488cfad1-ad70-411b-af99-de83626bd3d1.f2cd1c73-0d79-4c13-87a7-4394cbe0977b.prompt=Enter a value for emailFrom 488cfad1-ad70-411b-af99-de83626bd3d1.f36a5b9d-cafa-4c8e-bd49-05354adb1c56.prompt=Enter a value for emailTo 488cfad1-ad70-411b-af99-de83626bd3d1.f39bdd82-5cef-42d7-8e4f-75724219979c.transition.description=Recent email sent\: ${emailRecent} 488cfad1-ad70-411b-af99-de83626bd3d1.f642808a-1b51-4515-809d-741a13a20945.transition.description=Unable to send non-recent email. 488cfad1-ad70-411b-af99-de83626bd3d1.f69b410f-3379-4f49-a785-17dc83da7c6a.prompt=Enter a value for emailHost 488cfad1-ad70-411b-af99-de83626bd3d1.f87a0679-1ef7-427a-90d8-1a9e6bab1ad3.transition.description=Unable to send recent email. 488cfad1-ad70-411b-af99-de83626bd3d1.fc70a599-0b2d-40d6-b225-0d2f422d5316.transition.description=failed to compare date and times.
